9
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:31,275
Welcome to "Who Wants To Be A Millionaire"!

10
00:01:33,035 --> 00:01:35,000
Are you ready?

11
00:01:35,035 --> 00:01:37,765
Yes.

12
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:43,000
Please give a big round of applause
to a very first contestant of the night

13
00:01:43,035 --> 00:01:47,557
Jamal Malik from our very
own... (speaks Hindi) Mumbay!

14
00:01:50,035 --> 00:01:51,213
