15
00:02:00,071 --> 00:02:01,730
Smile, you'll be fine.

16
00:02:03,035 --> 00:02:05,965
Name.

17
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:11,388
Motherchud, name!

18
00:02:11,389 --> 00:02:13,165
Jamal Malik.

19
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:17,393
You have a name. Good. Stop crying.

20
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you very much.

21
00:02:26,035 --> 00:02:26,965
So, Jamal...

22
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:31,608
tell me something about yourself.

23
00:02:33,035 --> 00:02:36,000
I work in a call-center

24
00:02:36,035 --> 00:02:38,517
in Juhu. - Good.

25
00:02:38,552 --> 00:02:40,965
A phone basher..

26
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:44,000
